EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(PXCREATEDATETIME, '') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00' ELSE DATE_FORMAT(PXCREATEDATETIME, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') END AS PXCREATEDATETIME
CASE WHEN COALESCE(PXUPDATEDATETIME, '') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00' ELSE DATE_FORMAT(PXUPDATEDATETIME, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') END AS PXUPDATEDATETIME

CASE WHEN COALESCE(MODIFYDATE,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE (to_timestamp(SUBSTR(MODIFYDATE,1,4)||'-'||SUBSTR(MODIFYDATE,5,2)||'-'||SUBSTR(MODIFYDATE,7,2)||' '|| SUBSTR(MODIFYDATE,10,2)||':'||SUBSTR(MODIFYDATE,12,2)||':'||SUBSTR(MODIFYDATE,14,2)) ) END
